                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18090920-26-off147 t18090920-26-cd148"></join>, two shifts, value 4 s. two pair of stockings, value 1 s. a napkin, value 6 d. and a handkerchief, value 3 d.
